assessment by the point of diagnosis.</p><p><strong></strong></p>","North East Bedfordshire","Alistair Burt",,"2016-01-19T16:40:35.793Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/444220/answer","Biography information for Alistair Burt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/444220/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/444220/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2016-01-12","Mental Illness","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, how many people were diagnosed with (a) anxiety and (b) depression in each of the last five years.","false","Biography information for Jim Shannon","Strangford","Jim Shannon","22015"
